DIV.NAME: ALPHA
DIV.TITLE: Welcome!
DIV.META: Warning the Amazon Auction Creation Tool is currently in Beta testing mode. Please use at your own risk.

INPUT.NAME: merchant:amazon:login
INPUT.HELP: Please enter your Amazon Logon. This is always an E-mail address.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:title
INPUT.HELP: Enter a title for the auction item.

INPUT.NAME: product:zoovy:html
INPUT.HELP: Please enter a description for your auction item.

INPUT.NAME: product:zoovy:prod_image1
INPUT.HELP: Please click on browse to locate your image of the auction item. Image files must have an extension of .jpg, .png, or .gif to be accepted for upload.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:quantity
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate number of items you are selling.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:duration
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate the number of days between 2 and 14 that your auction should run.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:reserve
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate the lowest amount you are willing to accept for this item.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:sale_price
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate a price that the bidder could place to win the auction instantly.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:startprice
INPUT.HELP: Please enter the price bidding will start at.

INPUT.NAME: merchant:zoovy:payment_cashiers
INPUT.HELP: Please specify if you will accept a cashier check as payment for this item.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:ship_estimate
INPUT.HELP: Amazon requires you estimate the amount of shipping for this item to give bidders an idea, you will not be held to this number, but it should be close to the actual number.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:country
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate the Country location for this item.

INPUT.NAME: product:amazon:int_ship
INPUT.HELP: Please indicate if you are willing to ship this item internationally.
